sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_085_CSMS
    Note over CP,CS: Basic Authentication - Valid username/password combination
    Note over CP,CS: Prerequisite: Central System supports security profile 1 and/or 2

    CP->>CS: 1. HTTP Upgrade Request (without Authorization header)
    CS-->>CP: 2. Connection upgrade request REJECTED

    CP->>CS: 3. HTTP Upgrade Request (with Authorization header)
    Note left of CP: Authorization: Basic Base64(username:password)

    CS->>CS: Validate username/password
    CS-->>CP: 4. Accept connection upgrade request

    CP->>CS: 5. BootNotification.req
    CS-->>CP: 6. BootNotification.conf

    Note over CP,CS: [Send per connector and connectorId=0]
    CP->>CS: 7. StatusNotification.req
    CS-->>CP: 8. StatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP,CS: Tool validation - Password format: hex (32-40 chars) or plaintext UTF-8 (16-20 chars)
